Rogers" are among the events at the ninth annual Santa Barbara International 
Film Festival, March 4-13 at the Fiesta Theatre (916 State St.) and other 
nearby venues. More than 100 films will be screened in 10 days, and a 
screenwriting seminar is 1:30 p.m. March 5. (805) 963-0023. 
