speakers and competitions. 11 a.m.-9 p.m. Friday-Saturday; 11 a.m.-6 p.m. 
Sunday. Admission, $6; $3, seniors 55 and older; free for kids 12 and under. 
(714) 708-1543. 
</P>
<P>
 Call listed phone numbers for directions. MARY FRANCES SMITH 
