<TEXT>
<P>
 Regarding "Poolside in Palm Springs" (Jan. 30): 
</P>
<P>
 Those of us who reside in the beautiful desert love it all and welcome guests 
to show off the loveliness of it all.Although your article was interesting, it 
catered to the jet-set crowd, those who can well afford room rates of 
astronomical numbers. 
</P>
<P>
 Why not have a follow-up story that shows where the average traveler can go 
and still have money left over for dining out? Please understand that I'm not 
taking away anything from the places named in your article. It's just, who can 
afford them? 
</P>
<P>
 JANE BUSH, Palm Desert 
