</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 China announced a ban Friday on dumping radioactive waste at sea and said it 
would phase out sea disposal of industrial waste. 
</P>
<P>
 The ban takes effect today, the official Xinhua News Agency said. China 
previously allowed dumping of low-level radioactive waste at sea with 
