 * Many days I read in the newspaper of shootings and many other inhumanities.I 
feel the need to tell you about another brand of news. One night recently I 
went to see "Schindler's List" at the Cinemapolis in Anaheim Hills. The next 
morning, I realized I had lost my valuable watch, with the little diamonds all 
