<DATE>
<P>
February 20, 1994, Sunday, Bulldog Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 14; Column 1; Advance Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
474 words 
</P>
