 Kariya's asking price could climb if he does well, but that price is holding 
steady for now. "I'm seeing things here he's not getting away with that he's 
used to getting away with," Ferreira said. "This is a step up from the college 
level and the NHL is yet another step....The size thing won't be a problem 
because he's so quick and clever. He'll adjust." HELENE ELLIOTT 
