<TEXT>
<P>
 Strong free throw shooting led Thousand Oaks High to a 47-37 upset of Hart 
Saturday night in a second-round Division I-A game at Thousand Oaks. 
</P>
<P>
 Alissa Corey and Sara Samimi each scored 10 points for the Lancers (20-7), who 
made 16 of 29 free throws.Hart, the Foothill League champion, made only three 
of 13. 
</P>
<P>
 Buena 72, Downey 21 -- Mikko Giordano scored 22 points and the Bulldogs (21-2) 
outscored Downey, 25-3, in the third quarter of a Division I-A game at Buena. 
