Atkinson added 18 to lift the 49ers to victory at Reno. 
</P>
<P>
 Rod Hannibal had 13 points, 11 of them in the second half, and his 
three-pointer at 9:50 put Long Beach (13-8, 8-6) ahead for good, 56-55. 
</P>
