-- remain closed with the rest of the shopping center. Only one will be 
rebuilt. 
</P>
<P>
 Department stores: Bullock's and the Broadway, both closed. 
</P>
<P>
 Mall: No structural damage. Damage included cracks and broken tiles on walls; 
about 30% of storefronts broken; shattered, tempered glass at escalator 
railings and in the elevator. Closed. 
</P>
<P>
 Number of stores: 140 
</P>
<P>
